<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Truck Haulers Contact</title>

  <!-- Font Awesome CDN -->
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<%- include("partials/head") %>

<body >
  <!-- White background with dark text -->

  <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

  <section class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Contact Us</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>If you have any questions or inquiries, please feel free to reach out to us using the
          information
          below:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Corporate Office:</strong> Truck Haulers Ltd, Kannur, Kerala, India</li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 44 2222 3333</li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@Truck Haulers.com">info@Truck
              Haulers.com</a>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Fax:</strong> +91 44 2222 3344</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Our Commitment to Quality</h2>
        <p>Truck Haulers is committed to providing world-class vehicles and services that meet the
          highest
          standards of quality, performance, and reliability. Our engineering expertise and innovative
          solutions ensure that we are at the forefront of the automotive industry, delivering
          vehicles
          that
          exceed customer expectations.</p>

        <h2>Global Presence</h2>
        <p>With a strong global presence, Truck Haulers has established a reputation for providing
          exceptional
          transportation solutions across more than 50 countries. Our network of dealers, service
          centers,
          and
          manufacturing plants ensures that our customers receive support wherever they are located.
        </p>

        <h2>Customer Satisfaction</h2>
        <p>At Truck Haulers, customer satisfaction is at the core of everything we do. We strive to
          build
          long-lasting relationships with our clients by offering the best products and after-sales
          support.
          Our customer service team is always ready to assist with any inquiries or concerns you may
          have.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image Section -->
    <div class="text-center mt-5">
      <h2>Our Fleet</h2>
      <p>Take a look at some of the advanced vehicles we offer. We take pride in designing and
        manufacturing
        vehicles that are not only powerful but also safe and reliable for our customers.</p>

    </div>

    <!-- Contact Form -->
    <div class="card contact-form mt-5 py-4 px-4" style="background: #f8f9fa; color:black">
      <h2 class="mb-3">Send Us a Message</h2>
      <form action="/submit-message" method="POST">
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="name" class="form-label">Your Name:</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control border-primary" id="name" name="name" required>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email" class="form-label">Your Email:</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control border-primary" id="email" name="email" value="<%= user.email %>" readonly>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="subject" class="form-label">Subject:</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control border-primary" id="subject" name="subject" required>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="message" class="form-label">Message:</label>
          <textarea class="form-control border-primary" id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="background-color: #003366;">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Map Section (Optional) -->
    <div class=" my-3 container-fluid">
      <h2 class="p-2">Our Location</h2>
      <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3904.43477338131!2d75.37587895000001!3d11.87478425!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3ba43d3201e08ad9%3A0xf7a1d2cf129c6d76!2sCaltex%2C%20Kannur%2C%20Kerala!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1743501669326!5m2!1sen!2sin" width="100%" height="450" style="border:2px rgb(5, 5, 105) solid;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

           
<%- include("partials/scrollUp") %>

  <!-- Footer Section -->
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

  <!-- Bootstrap 5 JS and dependencies -->
  <%- include("partials/scripts") %>
</body>

</html>